opAccountSummary.balanceExpireDisclaimer: Great travel memories never expire, and now, miles don’t either. We’re excited to share that there’s no expiration date on the miles you’ve earned with us.
opAccountSummary.noMileageExpirationMessage: Great travel memories never expire, and now, miles don’t either. We’re excited to share that there’s no expiration date on the miles you’ve earned with us.
opAccountSummary.premierTrackerLearnAboutText:
• Premier qualifying flights: Premier qualifying flights (PQF) are based on the number of paid flight segments traveled on United, United Express®, and select airline partners

  • Premier qualifying points: Premier qualifying points (PQP) are based on the base fare and surcharge of flight purchases, along with most seating purchases and paid upgrades.

  • A minimum of four paid flight segments on United and/or United Express® is required in order to qualify for any Premier level. Certain exemptions apply.

  • Lifetime miles are earned based on the flight distance of United and United Express®-operated flights.

Full qualification terms and conditions

travelCreditInfo.travelCreditHeaderBody: You have travel credit to redeem.

travelCertificateTermsConditions.value:
Travel certificate

Travel certificates can be used for travel on United- and United Express®-operated flights. Any traveler can use a travel certificate, even if they weren't on the original itinerary. Learn more

Booking with a certificate

You can redeem a travel certificate for yourself and additional travelers when booking a flight on united.com or the United app.


When selecting your payment method, choose to apply a travel certificate and enter the year issued, your PIN code, and the last name on the certificate.

Future flight credit

You can use future flight credit for travel on United, United Express and partner-operated flights within 12 months of the date that your original ticket was issued. Learn more

Booking with future flight credit

Go to My Trips and under "Future flight credit," find the reservation and select "View details" to book a new trip using your flight credit.

futureFlightCreditDetails.text: You have future flight credit available. To use it, go to My Trips. Under "Find a reservation," enter the confirmation number and the last name for the reservation associated with the flight credit. Then select "Search" to view the Reservation Details for this credit.
futureFlightCreditDetails.multiFFCText: You have future flight credit available. To use it, search the trip's confirmation number on the Future Flight Credit screen.
